text: Yuliya Podskalnaya (born 18 April 1989) is a Russian female volleyball player. She was part of the Russian women's volleyball national team. She participated in the 2014 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2015 Montreux Volley Masters, and 2015 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship. == References == Category:Russian volleyball players Category:1989 births Category:Living people
